Beyond the walls of civilisation lies the Anarchy Grid, where Hostiles roam the wastelands and Crime is the only law. Here the LawBringers wage their endless battle to bring Law to the Lawless&hellip;
Built in a week for One Game a Month 2013, LawBringer is an action packed arcade blaster featuring gloriously retro 3D vector graphics and gratuitous particle abuse.
Enter the grid. Destroy all Hostiles. Bring Law to the Lawless.

Holy Crab! It&rsquo;s curry night, and Beerman&rsquo;s favourite curry house has been overrun by an an army of gentleman crabs!
But no top-hatted upper-class crustacean can come between Beerman and a vindaloo&hellip;
Guide our hero around the restaurant, collecting the curries and &lsquo;delivering&rsquo; them to the bathroom, but watch out for those swanky shellfish. If the heat gets too much, you can slow them down by leaving them a little &lsquo;present&rsquo;.
